de.tr7zw.nbtapi

Class NBTCompound

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tr7zw.nbtapi.NBTCompound
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadableNBT, ReadWriteNBT
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NBTContainer, NBTEntity, NBTFile, NBTItem, NBTListCompound, NBTPersistentDataContainer, NBTTileEntity

    public class NBTCompound
extends Object
implements ReadWriteNBT
    Base class representing NMS Compounds. For a standalone implementation check NBTContainer
    Author:
    tr7zw

        Note: the result will only contain data that is present in this readable nbt and is missing/different in the provided one.
